//MARK: Blog Context

- .map (loop through all blogs and edit a blog)
- .filter (to filter out/delete a blog)
- Exporting Context, Provider - with reducer, actions, initial state
- All actions declared and passed intp Custom Hooks
- Reducer declared and passed into Custom Hooks
- Initial state declared and passed into custom hooks
- Business logic to make changes to API 

//------------------------------------------------------------------
//MARK: Create Data Context 
(Custom Resusable Hook, Expects 3 args, return 1 object)

- Resusable Context & Provider
- Context.Provider passed to all children
- Exporting default function to return Context, Provider
- Send state and actions to children

